Quickstrike:







Quickstrike was getting nervous around the gather of bots. He kept a close 
optic on them. He didn't want to move. The pain in his leg was still biting 
at him, but it wasn't as bad if he moved it.

"Tell him t' get down here," he said to Hiss' group.
